{"tid":2365782,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★Airbnb：有不少人與衝擊國會有關，他們帳戶已被封鎖；FB：已加緊與執法部門交換消息","createTime":"2021-01-14T04:36:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T05:37:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9135dc8a497a99dce41fd2ca44f39114462c40e1","tid":2365782,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:36:52.000Z","msg":"Airbnb又表示，留意到有報道指有武裝民兵及右翼組織企圖進入華盛頓，干擾就職禮。平台會繼續確保該些成員不會成為Airbnb社群的一份子；又指平台曾調查登記名單，發現當中有不少人與右翼組織有關，或涉及上周三衝擊國會，他們帳戶已被封鎖。  社交平台Facebook亦向路透社透露，發現有愈來愈多跡象顯示，在總統就職禮前後會有更多暴力行為在不同日子出現。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFacebook指這些跡象包括宣傳數碼廣告，部分涉及武裝民兵或右翼組織，已加緊與執法部門交換消息及封鎖「停止盜竊」等特朗普支持者集會口號常用字眼。"},{"pid":"198d713370f779d98a2df7c55febb1fcb994c04f","tid":2365782,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30c059b527fb9a77de04a9b4a10053eaec7affd","tid":2365782,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:37:31.000Z","msg":"link<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/world/5fff7bb434b031f72c33240c/拜登就職禮下周舉行華盛頓加強保安-特朗普籲民眾冷靜\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fworld%2F5fff7bb434b031f72c33240c%2F%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E5%B0%B1%E8%81%B7%E7%A6%AE%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C%E8%8F%AF%E7%9B%9B%E9%A0%93%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E7%B1%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E5%86%B7%E9%9D%9C&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuA9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=5d548c8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/world/5fff7bb434b031f72c33240c/拜登就職禮下周舉行華盛頓加強保安-特朗普籲民眾冷靜</a>"},{"pid":"e74